NUMBER 3739
NAME Herbie's Hideaway, lawn deck
FOREST
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A lovely lush green lawn spreads out before you. A cottage sits to the
north, and a light mist drifts from a glass building that looks to be a
greenhouse on the west end of the lawn. A rosewood ramp leads up to the
pool deck to the east. A couple of colorful hammocks swings lazily between
the few miniature trees planted here. Raccoons can be seen playing in the
trees.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT ABOVE 2125
