NUMBER 3751
NAME Herbie's Hideaway, pool deck
OUTDOOR_OTHER
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
From here you can see the treehouse lawn and most of Grymwood over the
railings which surround the pool deck. The flooring and railings here are
all crafted in beautiful rosewood. On the southern side of the big pool is
a brick barbecue pit coupled with a large outdoor fireplace. Next to this
is a large outdoor dining table surrounded by a wraparound bench. Colorful
paper lanterns hang from all the railings.
*DESCRIPTION_END
