NUMBER 3752
NAME Herbie's Hideaway Greenhouse
OUTDOOR_OTHER
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
It is hard to see very far through this humid mist. All around you is a
great variety of extremely healthy plants and colorful blossoms. In the
center is a huge soil test bed, filled with different soils. Each soil
type is separated from the sample next to it by strips of rosewood board.
Across the room, a set of shelves stand against the wall. There is a
drain in the floor, a large mirmach door with a panel on the northern
wall, and a glass arch to the east.
*DESCRIPTION_END

