NUMBER 3754
NAME Giant Rosewood Tree, lower platform
FOREST
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are on a platform porch of sorts build high up onto the side of this
giant tree. Although you can see the path way below, you cannot see much
else as you are surrounded by trees on all sides. Looking much further up
the ladder you see an opening in the forest canopy. A swing has been
installed here for your rest before you continue the journey.
*DESCRIPTION_END

